    "Applications of AI in tumor metabolomics.",
    "AI technologies play crucial roles in various stages of tumor metabolomics research, including experimental design, data preprocessing, metabolite annotation, data analysis and omics integration, and clinical applications.",
    "Three AI technologies -machine learning, deep learning, and natural language processing-contribute significantly to each stage.",
